 work on your new amazing shoot'em up.
 - your cat has eaten the disk containing FinalWrapper and got ill.
 - your local power plant broke down while using FinalWrapper (a known bug, which
 only occurs very rarely)!
 -  you  cannot close  your  mouth  any more because of sheer amazement about the
